From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Galileo CSM Workspace <galileo-csm@example.invalid>
Date: Tue, 21 Apr 2026 17:45:00 -0600
Subject: [PATCH] SeaBIOS: expose USB storage through CSM BBS

In CSM mode, discover USB storage while handling Legacy16UpdateBbs,
export the discovered SeaBIOS USB drives into the BBS table, and reapply
BBS priorities to SeaBIOS boot entries during PrepareToBoot. This lets
UEFI boot managers enumerate and select the same real USB disk that
SeaBIOS will boot through INT 13h.

